{
  "stem": "21582.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- but apparently, she thought that there was a little bit too much noise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she took out one young woman as a hostage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, if I hear a whisper, I'll beat her to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew she would.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so of course, there was silence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, we were banished to this punishment barrack, as though this one wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For some reason-- and I don't know if she took a liking to us, but on some level, she, I think, liked us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that, too, is kind of annoying to me because so often, if somebody would show a glance of humanity, we'd say, oh, they like us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, they are not really so bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But, you know, bad people have their good moments, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So maybe we just caught her at a good moment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, she kind of-- my sister didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She needed, really, to recover a little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were no selections during that, that small period of recovery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my sister remained in camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my-- and I-- and my mother and I went to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "While my mother and I were gone, my sister-- a, a, a, a man from Skarzysko, from a labor camp, a German, came over.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he told them that-- and he, he announced that he needs some people to work at HASAG, a, a ammunition camp in Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My sister said he sounded [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] believable-- also because she wanted to believe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, so her name-- she-- her name was put on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But my mother and I were gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, she, she didn't know-- but everybody believed 'you don't believe it anyway.' They are taking the people to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So people wanted to trade places.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
